Tshikwama, tshe tsha kuvhanganya R2.61 biḽioni u swika zwino, tsho thusa kha u wana PPE dzine dza ḓo thusa kha sisiṱeme dza mutakalo wa tshitshavha na vhashumeli vha mutakalo wa tshitshavha lwa miṅwedzi Fhedziha, hu dzulela u vha na ṱhahelelo ya PPE u mona na ḽifhasi, hu tshi katelwa na Afrika Tshipembe.
