Minisṱa Vho Mkhize vho ri “ri khou swikisa khuwelelo kha vhashumeli vha zwa dzilafho, na avho vho nothaho, uri vha ḓe vha tholiwe – naho hu tshi tou vha lwa tshifhinga tshiṱuku.
